{"tid":1722381,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]每個人嘅發言數據，密碼重設","createTime":"2019-11-15T01:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:32:45.000Z","uid":138613,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c25ea07cffd05051891789d91ca30c11371d2353","tid":1722381,"uid":138613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:22:29.000Z","msg":"鑑於近日有太多惡意會員刻意製造混亂<br />\n以求帶風向等<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以係每個會員嘅起底頁面加啲數據<br />\n等起佢底嘅會員自行判斷有關會員是否有古怪<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<br />\n會員A<br />\n<br />\n總發言次數：xxxx (用嚟知佢是否活躍)<br />\n總開post次數：<br />\n日均發言次數：xx (佢平日上連登嘅習慣)<br />\n日均開post次數：<br />\n今日發言數目：x (如果今日突然大增/大減，違反平日上連登習慣，即為有古怪)<br />\n今日開post次數：<br />\n最後留言日期：xx/xx/2019 (以顯示有冇突然上水)<br />\n最後開post日期<br />\n今日推post次數：x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要識別用咗幾次&quot;push&quot;,&quot;推&quot;，icon等冇meaning嘅手法推post)<br />\n今日開post次數：<br />\n今個月/今年嘅推post數：xx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原理同上)<br />\n今個月/今年嘅開post數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;最後留言日期&rdquo;方面，可以畀會員自行選擇幾耐唔上水／留言就重設密碼，保障自己，以防有人偷手機偷埋acc<br />\n重設密碼方法可以set 自己email/另一會員email<br />\n咁自己唔見手機都可以拜託個朋友幫手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗下是否可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10405bc0bde02a875d4f27680600dec4b33a2386","tid":1722381,"uid":138613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:29:35.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a06d166f6312de14b5697a2400e7e18012862a9","tid":1722381,"uid":110653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一撚早要啦, 咁撚得閒整班堆表情都唔知做wt7<br />\n其他論壇個個都有呢D功能"},{"pid":"4f5096483d6ec282d434fa2e33eb5a31cc23bcab","tid":1722381,"uid":138613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}